About Event

​Ring in 2026 with a casual cocktail mixer on Stanford campus—meet fellow students, founders, and tech folks, and enjoy a fun night of games and good vibes.

​🗓 Time: Dec 31, 2025, 10:00 PM – Jan 1, 2026, 1:00 AM

📍 Location: Stanford University (exact address will be shared after RSVP)

👥 Who it’s for: Stanford students/ Founders/ Tech Professionals

​🍸 We provide: cocktails + light bites

​♠️ What’s happening:

​New Year wishes (wish wall / sharing)

​A fun personality quiz

​Boar
